\DOC catch_signal

\TYPE {catch_signal : ('a signal -> ('a -> unit) -> unit)}

\SYNOPSIS
Associate a function with a signal.

\LIBRARY window

\DESCRIBE
Evaluating the function {catch_signal sig fun} means that in future
whenever signal {sig} is raised with argument {a}, the expression
{fun a} will be evaluated.

\SEEALSO
clear_signal, new_signal

\ENDDOC
